Package: covidExplorer
Title: Contains a Shiny App with summaries,analytics and news about COVID-19
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Panagiotis",
           family = "Stylianos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pete.styl@gmail.com"
           )
Description: The package deploys a shiny app that allows users to interactively
        browse data regarding the spread of COVID-19 in various countries. The
        original purpose of the app is to offer a summary of information regarding 
        COVID-19 with emphasis being given on new cases and latest implemented 
         measures. Figures in the Measures tab can be exported as png images.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    shiny
